-- Sourced from official .gov statutes 2026-06-11; every value cited + independently verified
-- against the quoted statute text before seeding. Provisions attach to each state's 'residential'
-- act; a topic absent for a state = no statutory value exists (NOT invented). Hedged + dated +
-- disclaimered at surface time per the S442 posture. States: NC, MI, NJ, VA, WA, MA, TN, IN, MD, MO.
